<ul>
<li>Applying for an OnDeck loan is simple and fast</li>
<li>We’ve already delivered over $4 billion to small businesses</li>
<li>OnDeck is a publicly traded company with a Better Business Bureau rating of A+</li>
<li>We make loans from $5,000 to $500,000</li>
</ul>
